@NODE "contact" "PFS-Defrag - Contact/Support"
@TOC "contents"
@{B}CONTACT/SUPPORT INFORMATION@{UB}

I hope you find this useful!  Please e-mail me with your comments, reports or
suggestions.  Please also pay the website a visit some time.

If you are reporting a bug then please e-mail me the 4 log files produced in
RAM: (attach them to your mail as 4 separate files or archive them into one
lha file please).  They are named "dvoutput", "dverroroutput", "fragoutput"
and "defragoutput".  If you can provide a log of all the output that appears
in the window then that is very useful too.

  Keith Halstead
  pfsdefrag@halsteadk.freeserve.co.uk
  http://www.halsteadk.freeserve.co.uk/pfsdefrag/

Get Opus Cut'n'Paste from
http://www.halsteadk.freeserve.co.uk/cutnpaste/

@{" Return to Contents " LINK "contents"}
@ENDNODE
